- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is another possible category as lambda-calculus is a fundamental concept in programming languages and the paper deals with evaluation in lambda-calculus.
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with the implementation of effective samplers for combinatorial structures.
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is also less likely but possible as lambda-calculus is a topic in formal languages and the paper deals with the quantitative properties of environments and closures.
